view.name: DHS Daily Report
view.description: This dataset includes the daily number of families and individuals residing in the Department of Homeless Services (DHS) shelter system and the daily number of families applying to the DHS shelter system.

columns.description: The number of children in families with children in shelter as of the date of census

columns.name: Total Individuals in Shelter
columns.description: The number of single adults, individuals in adult families, and adults and children in families with children in shelter as of the date of census

columns.name: Total Single Adults in Shelter
columns.description: The number of single adult men and women in shelter as of the date of census
